08:27.375 --> 08:29.375
- [laughs]

08:29.458 --> 08:30.833
- And me.

08:30.916 --> 08:33.583
- I'm just gonna try
to speak from the heart.

08:33.666 --> 08:35.833
And, um...

08:37.250 --> 08:39.583
You know,
the Dory that I remember

08:39.666 --> 08:42.166
was the...

08:42.250 --> 08:45.208
sweetest person
