08:46.750 --> 08:49.250
And I'm not too good at
speaking, you know,

08:49.333 --> 08:51.541
so I'm just gonna, um...

08:51.625 --> 08:53.083
try to do what--

08:53.166 --> 08:56.708
what Dory hated the most,
and, um...

08:56.791 --> 09:00.083
