10:45.125 --> 10:46.375
- Honestly,
I don't even wanna know.

10:46.458 --> 10:47.833
- [babbles]
- Oh, my God.

10:47.916 --> 10:49.208
- Hey, Marc.
- Hey.

10:49.291 --> 10:50.875
- I gotta go.
- No, no, Portia, no.

10:50.958 --> 10:53.083
Oh, Portia.
No.

10:53.166 --> 10:54.500
- Hi.

10:54.583 --> 10:57.166
I really liked your speech.

10:57.250 --> 10:59.375
- Thank you.
Thank you.

10:59.458 --> 11:01.625
Thanks for coming.
- Of course.

11:01.708 --> 11:04.875
Dory was...ahead of her time.

11:06.125 --> 11:09.000
- She--she was, yeah.

11:09.083 --> 11:10.208
