13:13.916 --> 13:16.708
I was asleep in my armchair

13:16.791 --> 13:20.541
with my mouth open,
and um...

13:20.625 --> 13:22.458
I woke up

13:22.541 --> 13:23.875
to Dory kissing me.

13:23.958 --> 13:26.708
♪ ♪

13:26.791 --> 13:27.875
- What?

13:27.958 --> 13:31.250
- I promise you both
it happened.

