And, um, it begs the question:

13:36.375 --> 13:38.750
Did she ever try to kiss you?

13:38.833 --> 13:41.291
- Did Dory try to kiss us?
- Yeah.

13:41.375 --> 13:43.291
- She kissed both of us.

13:43.375 --> 13:47.041
- Oh, God, I knew it.
I knew it.

13:47.125 --> 13:49.708
