13:49.791 --> 13:51.833
I just--I don't mean to be
disrespectful,

13:51.916 --> 13:56.291
but I do think that
we have a case here.

13:57.500 --> 13:59.250
- It's good to see you.

13:59.333 --> 14:02.250
[indistinct chatter]

14:02.333 --> 14:05.500
♪ ♪

14:05.583 --> 14:08.250
- Portia, I'm gonna head out.

14:08.333 --> 14:12.583
- Thanks for coming, Mom.
It was nice of you.

14:12.666 --> 14:15.750
- I...

14:15.833 --> 14:17.500
I'm sorry.

14:17.583 --> 14:19.916
- Yeah, thank you.
I know, it sucks.

14:20.000 --> 14:21.166
- Not about Dory.

14:21.250 --> 14:23.583
I mean, of course about Dory.

14:24.916 --> 14:26.708
But about everything.

14:28.333 --> 14:33.125
I think I've always been
